section.t:
The request Repr-Digest field-value is computed on the enclosed representation (see
), which is the JSON object {"title": "New
Title"} followed by an LF.

figure.sourcecode:
NOTE: '\' line wrapping per RFC 8792
HTTP/1.1 200 OK Content-Type: application/json Repr-Digest: \ sha-256=:RK/0qy18MlBSVnWgjwz6lZEWjP/lF5HF9bvEF8FabDg==:
{"hello": "world"}

